From b55608b953e1bdf852aa41ef4ac897a75a9b7d4f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Song Gao <gaosong@loongson.cn>
Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2026 10:42:15 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 150/587] FROMLIST: LoongArch: KVM: Add dmsintc inject msi to
 the dest vcpu

Implement irqfd deliver msi to vcpu and vcpu dmsintc inject irq.
Add irqfd choice dmsintc to set msi irq by the msg_addr and
implement dmsintc set msi irq.

Signed-off-by: Song Gao <gaosong@loongson.cn>

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/loongarch/20260409024215.136932-1-gaosong@loongson.cn/
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
---
